                <h3>What you have to know about Redmine Observer</h3>

                <br>
                <img src="/img/rmobserver/pad_and_phone2_6.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="">
                <br>

                The application has the following features:

                <ul>
                    <li>Working offline with the most essential functions</li>
                    <li>Working with more than one Redmine source simultaneously</li>
                    <li>Receiving notification of new issues and issues, where changes were made</li>
                    <li>Forming local groups for issues</li>
                    <li>Making reports for the time spent offline</li>
                    <li>Searching in all sources simultaneouslyand much more…</li>
                </ul>

            </div>
