                <h3>Smart caching</h3>

                <img src="/img/rmobserver/pad-1.png" class="img-responsive" alt="">
                <br>
                <ul>
                    <li>The application automatically updates the issue, finds changes and new issues assigned to the user, as well as uploads tracks on the server and downloads the rest of the tracks for further analysis in the background</li>
                    <li>Additionally, recently viewed objects and issues in the local groups are stored locally. They can always be opened without a network connection</li>
                    <li>The interface is structured to allow quick access to the information you need</li>
                    <li>The search is performed simultaneously on all sources</li>
                    <li>Each issue can be opened in the web without going to browser</li>
                </ul>
            </div>


        </div>

        <hr>
